sentences: Ida Kristina Sand (born 5 November 1977) is a Swedish jazz singer and pianist.
She debuted as a guest artist at Nils Landgrens Christmas with My Friends in 2006 releasing her solo debut album  Meet Me Around Midnight in 2007.
